videos.description: Chandler Hutchison drives to the basket and finishes after getting fouled by Illinois State's Phil Fayne.
videos.headline: Boise State's Hutchison pulls off nice crossover for layup

videos.description: Christian Sengfelder makes three nice 3-point buckets for the Boise State in the first 10 minutes of play against Illinois State.
videos.headline: Sengfelder knocking in 3's for Boise State

videos.description: Jerron Martin finds Phil Fayne under the basket and Fayne takes it to the rim to finish with a nice two-handed dunk for the Redbirds.
videos.headline: Illinois State's Martin feeds Fayne for two-handed jam
